<h2>Agra &amp;¬†The Taj Mahal</h2>
Agra can also refer to the administrative district that has its headquarters in Agra city. It is a major tourist destination because of its many splendid Mughal-era buildings, most notably the <strong>TƒÅj Mahal, Agra Fort and Fatehp≈´r Sikrƒ´</strong>, all three of which are <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Heritage_Site" target="_blank">UNESCO World Heritage Sites</a>.

